    <item>
      <title>Design peer reviews to support our team growth</title>
      <link>https://maxence-d5f05.firebaseapp.com/blog/posts/design-peer-reviews-to-support-our-team-growth/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2019 11:31:33 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://maxence-d5f05.firebaseapp.com/blog/posts/design-peer-reviews-to-support-our-team-growth/</guid>
      <description>Illustration by Jetty Cho
I always hope to see my teammates collaborate more. Now that we are at a stage of faster growth, more fellow designers are going to join us and it felt like a good timing to push forward this all peer-review strategy.
It’s never too late. We’ve been a team of 4 designers for the last 2 years, including 2 product / 2 visual designers. Collaboration &amp;amp; Review have been naturally there as soon as the team got 2 product designers, but it’s never been a thing across the entire team, probably due to the fact that some of our designers are working remotely, bringing communication issues.</description>
    </item>
    
